I am a software manager and need weekly or even daily reports on my developers. Now that I will be working with a consulting firm, I want to be able to track their involvement, too. I love the tool; however, it lacks strongly in the reporting department. Here is my requirement:

To able to view a status report for a given developer (or a summary report for a selected list of developers) in a given time period (weekly, monthly, daily, etc.) The status report should show which tasks he has completed, how much time he has spent, which ones are in progress and their due dates. I want to be able to understand what a particular developer has worked across all projects, components, etc.

